Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:20.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}As you wish, I will gamble with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:20.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}nozomidoori ni kakete ageru {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:23.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}I won't go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:23.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}tekagen wa shinai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:27.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Love, hate, love, hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:27.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}suki kirai suki kirai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:30.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Who will be first?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:30.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}saisho wa dare? {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:34.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Moderation is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:34.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}hodohodo ja tsumannai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:37.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}It's all or nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:37.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}subete ka zero ka {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:40.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Love, hate, love, hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:40.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}suki kirai suki kirai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:44.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:44.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}tanoshimimashou {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:55.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}It feels good when you indulge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:55.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}nomerikomu hou ga kimochi ii {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:02:03.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}I'll live, live, live, live a story of wonderful thrills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:02:03.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}suteki na suriru no sutoorii wo ikiru ikiru ikiru ikiru {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:10.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}We won't lose anything of importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:10.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}ushinau mono wa takaga shireteru {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:17.43,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}We may lose our tomorrow, but not our whole future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:17.43,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}ashita wo nakushitemo mirai ga nakunarutte wake janai {\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:23.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}If you want to dream, you need to be world-weary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:23.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}yume wo miru ni wa shirisugita jidai sa{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:28.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}Come here, and gather round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:28.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}oide yo kono yubi tomare{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:32.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,400)}I prefer to love until there's nothing left.
