Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:43.78,Default2,chapter,0,0,0,Part 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hyakkao Private Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:53.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,{創立122年を迎える\N伝統と格式を誇る学園}The school prides itself on 122 years of tradition and class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:59.74,Default2,,0,0,0,,{でも この名門校には\N絶対的な階級制度がある}However, at this prestigious academy, there is an absolute hierarchy of students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:04.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,Your rank is not determined by grades or athleticism
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:13.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,but by your gambling prowess alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,Most students here are caught up in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:24.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,the cycle of winning, losing, and betting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:27.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,But I met someone motivated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:29.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,not by money or fame,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:33.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,but by her desire to gamble itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.73,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko Jabami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:38.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,Ever since she arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:42.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,{百花王学園のギャンブルは\N確実に狂気の度を増した}the gambling at Hyakkao Academy has become noticeably crazier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:47.65,Default2,,0,0,0,,And right now, at this very moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:51.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,{身を焦がすようなギャンブルに\Nその身を委ねている}Yumeko is letting herself be consumed by her gambling lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:02.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Jabami. Miss Ikishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,What is your response?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:07.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,You have the right to step away from this gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:15.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,{あまりにもギャンブルが過酷すぎて\N返事もできないようね}My game is so horrifying that they can't even speak, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,You did spook me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:23.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,My mind went blank there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:27.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, if you're that frightened, I guess I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,The game will—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,{both}Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,{極限までシンプル\Nそれでいて極限の駆け引き}Extreme in its simplicity,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,{極限までシンプル\Nそれでいて極限の駆け引き}yet extreme in its strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted a gamble like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:43.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,The rules are great, but this machine is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:48.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,{失敗すりゃ 問答無用で\Nぶった切られる この感じ}It'll slice you apart as soon as you slip up, no bones about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:48.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:54.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,I just brushed it and it drew blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:57.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,Heh heh heh. You've got this thing damn sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yumeko, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:02.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful, Suzui?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,Uh... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's with these two?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:14.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could they really not be afraid of my game?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's unthinkable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:21.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,{見慣れた肉体を失うことは\N根源的な恐怖のはず\i1}Losing a precious body part is a fundamental human fear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:24.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,Very well. Let us begin, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:25.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,With your affirmative responses, I officially recognize this gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you even call this gambling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:39.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,{運も知略も関係ない\N必要なのは無謀な勇気だけだ} {\i1}It doesn't matter how lucky or smart you are. All you need for this game is reckless abandon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:44.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,{でも 夢子も生志摩も\Nそう簡単に指は抜かない\i1}But neither Yumeko nor Ikishima will pull their fingers out so easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,H-hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:47.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:50.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,You're the one who rigged up this guillotine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:54.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,So don't you know which string is connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,If so, it's hardly a fair game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:01.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,{益体(やくたい)もないことしか言えないなら\N口を閉じてなさい ザコ}If you don't have anything useful to say, keep your mouth shut, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kid...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,The string that connects to the blade
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:08.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,can easily be changed by opening this box.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll have the dealer switch the string.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,That will satisfy you, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:14.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:19.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,{あんたが特定の誰かを\N勝たせることも可能になるけど}it will be possible for {\i1}you{\i0} to determine who wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:19.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Mushibami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:24.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, that is altogether unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,{我々 選挙管理委員会は} The Election Management Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:29.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,{絶対中立であることに\N誇りを持っている}takes pride in its absolute neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:33.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,{そうでなければ\Nこんな仕事 何の意味もない}If not, our jobs would be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:38.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,{選挙管理委員会を\Nナメないでいただきたい}Please do not insult the Election Management Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:39.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,How very trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,Well, fine then. Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:54.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,{なんだよ 随分 慎重だな\N誰も見たりしねえのによ}What's the point of being so careful when nobody's gonna sneak a peek anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,Peeking takes away half the fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.44,Default2,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's been so long since I've felt this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（鈴井）\Nハハ… 夢子が あからさまに\N人を嫌うなんて珍しいな\i1}Heh. It's unusual for Yumeko to flaunt her distaste for someone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:09.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not that I blame her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,Do you understand the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,{僅か数分後には\Nこの中の誰かの指が}In just a few short minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:19.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,{宙を舞っているかもしれない\Nってことを}one of our fingers could be dancing in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:26.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,{準備完了であります\Nどうぞ皆様 お入りください}Preparations are complete. Please come in, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,Ahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:31.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm getting tired of waiting. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:32.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Yamata?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:37.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,Did you do a thorough inspection?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:42.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,{ギャンブルを心から楽しむためには\N必要なことですから}We won't be able to fully enjoy the game if you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,I most certainly did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,{あの高さから落ちた勢いで\N刃が当たれば} If the blade falls from that height,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:50.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,{まず間違いなく\N切断されるでありましょう}amputation will be unavoidable if it hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,Heh heh heh. Just what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're going to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now, then, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:02.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,{チップを賭け\N指をギロチンに挿し込んでください}Place your chips, and insert your fingers into the guillotine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（鈴井）\Nあの刃は本物\N蟲喰はホントに分かってるのか？\i1}That blade is the real deal. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（鈴井）\Nあの刃は本物\N蟲喰はホントに分かってるのか？\i1}Does Mushibami really know what she's doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does she know how dangerous—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,The Finger-Cutting Guillotine game will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let me go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:24.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,You don't mind, do you? I can't hold back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,Sure. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,Our odds are the same, no matter who cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:32.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,Then, Miss Ikishima, the first move is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. Thanks for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.18,Default2,,0,0,0,,Which one'll be it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:41.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,{指が落ちるかの瀬戸際だ\Nよ〜く考えねえと}Our fingers are riding on this one little moment—I've gotta think it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:47.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,This is too much, Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:52.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy I get to gamble with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,Heh. Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:03.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,{今度は お互いだ\Nお互いが20分の１で指を落とす}We're on equal footing now. Same one-in-20 chance to lose a finger for both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:06.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let's feel the pain together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:07.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:11.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,Guess it wouldn't happen on the first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:16.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,I see. That was a miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:20.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,{降参する方は\Nいつでも指を抜いてください}You may take your finger out at any time, if you wish to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,It appears no one is surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:29.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,{では 次 ２手目\N蛇喰夢子様 どうぞ}In that case, Miss Yumeko Jabami, the second move is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:34.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,{まだ紐が多いからといって\N油断はできませんね}There are quite a few strings left, but I shouldn't be careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.59,Default2,,0,0,0,,{その瞬間は いつも突然やって来る}The moment of truth could come at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,Heh. True that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:44.46,Default2,,0,0,0,,{よそ見してるうちに終わったら\N大損だ}You'll really pay for it if you're looking away when it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:45.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,Well, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,Guess that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:57.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（恵利美）\Nこいつら まだ確率が低いとはいえ\N随分あっさり切ったな\i1}Even though the odds are still low,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（恵利美）\Nこいつら まだ確率が低いとはいえ\N随分あっさり切ったな\i1}these girls cut their strings without any fuss.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,{話には聞いていた蛇喰夢子は\Nともかく…\i1}I've heard about Yumeko Jabami already, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:07.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,You—your name was Midari Ikishima, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:11.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why did you join this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:17.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,{あなたは蛇喰夢子に\N敗れたことがあると聞いたわ}I heard that you lost to Yumeko Jabami once already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:22.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,{自分の指を賭してまで\N蛇喰夢子とギャンブルをするのは}So, the reason you'd risk a finger just to gamble with Yumeko Jabami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:25.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,{もしかして 復讐(ふくしゅう)のつもりかしら？} Could it be revenge, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,Revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:31.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yeah... it might just be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:34.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,She got me so hot and bothered...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now I need some real bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:37.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:42.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,{お前が当たりを引いても\N文句は言わねえよ}I'm not gonna complain, even if you snip the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,{何せ\Nこの場を用意してくれた恩人だ}You're the one who made this all happen, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,No need to remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Another miss, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,Haha! This is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,Heh. It sure is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:09.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,{一手一手(いっていって)\Nじっくり危険が迫るのも 乙なもの}The danger steadily increasing as we take our turns—it's sublime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:12.11,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（妄）\Nなんだよ 夢子もそう思うか？}What, you think so too, Yumeko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:15.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,{あたしたち\Nやっぱり気が合うよな}We really do have a connection!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:18.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,{さて それはどうでしょうね}Oh, I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:20.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:24.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,{この２人\N少なくとも虚勢を張る度胸はある\i1}At the very least, these girls have the nerve to keep up the bravado.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:28.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how much longer they can hold out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:32.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be watching from a position of safety!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because this guillotine, you see,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:39.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,{絶対に指を切断しないように\Nなっているんですもの\i1}is designed to never really amputate anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:44.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,{この台には鉄板が仕込んであって\N刃が落ちても指に届く前に止まる\i1}There's an iron plate in this platform that stops the blade from falling all the way down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:48.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{そして これはイカサマではない}Best of all, it's not actually cheating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:52.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,{指に達しないだけで\N刃は確かに落ちるのだから\i1}The blade still falls—even if it doesn't reach our fingers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:56.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,{ディーラーは もちろん\N確認したときに気付いただろうが\i1}The dealer must have noticed when she inspected the machine,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,{ルールに反していないのだから\N黙認する\i1}but since it's not a violation of the rules, she'll stay quiet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:03.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{絶対中立というのは本当らしい}That bluster about "absolute neutrality" seems to be real.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:07.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,{結論として\Nあんたたちの勝ちは絶対にない\i1}And as a result, there's no way either of you can win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:10.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,{唯一 刃が落ちるまで耐えれば\N引き分けられるが\i1}If they can hold out until the blade falls, they might manage a tie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:17.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,{１手ずつ迫る恐怖心に\N耐えるだけの器はあるかしら？\i1}But can either of them withstand a terror that increases turn by turn?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,Damn, I got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:25.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,{夢子 頼む\Nそろそろ当たりを引いてくれ}Yumeko, please! Cut the right one, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:30.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,I wonder which one it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:35.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,{しかし こんなすてきな道具を\Nなぜ所有されていたのですか？}But if I may, why do you possess this wonderful device?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,You must have had it before coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:43.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（妄）\Nウへッ 確かにな\N何に使うんだよ こんなもん}Oh... good point. What do you normally use this thing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,Torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:50.15,Default2,,0,0,0,,{それが私の家\N蟲喰家が代々引き継ぐ稼業なの}That is the Mushibami family business, passed down through the generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,Torture? In this day and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:55.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,It is needed in every age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:13:00.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,{この子を使って 一本一本\N紐を順にゆっくり切っていくとね}When you hook someone up to this little beauty and start cutting the strings one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:05.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,{誰でも どんなことでも\N面白いようにしゃべるの}They'll happily tell you whatever you want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:08.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,{あなたたちは\Nどこまで耐えられるかしらね}I wonder how long you two will last.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:13.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,{へえ〜 世の中\Nいろいろなお仕事があるんですね}Wow. There really is a job for everything, isn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:18.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,{でも それなら話が早い}But that makes things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:18.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:22.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（夢子）\N自分が業とすることを\N人にされたからといって}If someone did to you what you do to others as your profession...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,{文句のあるはずもない}You'd have no right to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:28.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,{ましてや\Nご自分から申し出たギャンブル}Especially since you proposed this gamble yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,{“指なんて惜しくない”\Nとは言い過ぎにしても}It's not that you don't mind losing a finger,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,{“失うことも やむなし”\Nですよね？}But that you have accepted it as a potential necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.42,Default2,,0,0,0,,{“失うことも やむなし”\Nですよね？}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:39.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,Miss Yamata?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.22,Default2,,0,0,0,,{ちゃんと\N取り外していただけましたね？}You did remove it for us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:49.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,{ああ 無論であります\N任務でありますから}Oh, most certainly! That is my job, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:55.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,{心からギャンブルを楽しむことが\Nできそうですね}Now I can enjoy the game with no reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:14:00.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,{おいおい 何の話だよ\N仲間外れにすんなよ〜}Hey, whatcha talking about? Don't leave me hanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,Now, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:07.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, wait. Hold on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:09.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did she say just now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.83,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Did you remove it?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This device has no removable parts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:23.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:27.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Another miss, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,{しっかし いいこと聞いたぜ\N拷問が仕事だって？}But that's real interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:32.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,{しっかし いいこと聞いたぜ\N拷問が仕事だって？}Torturing people is your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:36.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,That means you'd have no qualms {あたしを躊躇(ちゅうちょ)なく\N痛めつけてくれるってことだよな}giving my finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,{あたしを躊躇(ちゅうちょ)なく\N痛めつけてくれるってことだよな}giving me the torment I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,{そりゃいい\Nお前の番だぞ 蟲喰！}I love it! It's your turn, Mushibami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,{さっさとやってくれ！}Give it to me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（夢子）さあ どうぞ 遠慮なく}It's all you! Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\frz2}{\fs66.667}Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\frz-2}{\fs66.667}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fs80}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:55.57,Current Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(963.556,652.889)}Episode 1:\NThe Women Who Went\NAll In Again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:55.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fs63.333}Let's go all in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:25.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,{６手目 蟲喰様 外れであります}That was turn six, Miss Mushibami. A miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:30.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,God, I can't get enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:34.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,{紐が少なくなると\Nどんどんスリルが増すな}The more strings we cut, the bigger the thrill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,Quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:39.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My wager was 100% safe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:44.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,{相手の恐れおののく姿を\N一方的に鑑賞するだけの拷問\i1}I should be watching my opponents tremble in fear from a position of safety.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how it's supposed to be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:51.76,Default2,,0,0,0,,{どうやって気付いた？\N装置の中の鉄板に\i1}How did they find out about the iron plate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.26,Default2,,0,0,0,,{それとも ただのハッタリか？\Nディーラーとグルになって\i1}Or is it just a bluff?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:56.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,{それとも ただのハッタリか？\Nディーラーとグルになって\i1}Is the dealer in on it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:16:00.27,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{芽生えた疑念を払拭(ふっしょく)する術(すべ)はない}I have no way of erasing these doubts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,{これは\N私が用意したギャンブルだから\i1}I came up with this game in the first place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:07.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,{私から疑義を呈するのは\N細工を認めることと同じ\i1}If I ask a question, I'll be admitting to my trick.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:10.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{私は私自身に縛られている}I've been hoisted by my own petard!{\i0}{TL note: Could be "I have no one to blame but myself" if you think this is too esoteric}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:13.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,{生志摩さん 早く次にいきましょう}Ikishima, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:16.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:19.25,Default2,,0,0,0,,H-here I go, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:23.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,Ahahaha! Ahahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,I get it now, Yumeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:30.20,Default2,,0,0,0,,{あたしが間違ってた\N全員でひとつのリスクを負う}I had it wrong before. We all take on the same risk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:32.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,This is so much fun, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:41.31,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（恵利美）\Nおかしいだろ\Nなぜ お前らは紐を切り続ける\i1}I don't understand. How can you keep cutting the strings?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:45.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,{私の細工に気付いたなら\Nそれがハッタリであろうとも\i1}You could have had the game canceled as soon as you saw my trick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.98,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you were just bluffing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:51.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,{そうしないのは こいつら\N心からこのギャンブルを…\i1}The reason you didn't must be that...\NYou truly want to do this...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,Your turn, Miss Mushibami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（妄）おい あんまり焦らすなよ\N（恵利美）なんなの…}Hey, don't tease us too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.69,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（妄）おい あんまり焦らすなよ\N（恵利美）なんなの…}{\i1}{\an8}W-what's with them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:16:59.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:06.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the matter with this school?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:22.89,Default2,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:27.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,{おいおい\Nなんだよ ワケ分かんねえ}Hey, what's your deal all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:32.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,{お前が用意したギャンブルやって\Nなんで お前が泣いてんだよ？}Why would you start crying about the game you came up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mushibami...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.85,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{だから やめさせたかったんだ}That's why I wanted to stop this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:46.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,{このギャンブルは\N最初から この２人には通用しない\i1}This gamble would never faze either of them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Particularly Yumeko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:49.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because she's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:10.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,The world runs on ups and downs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:10.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}appu daun wa yo no tsune
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:13.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,I won't let one bad hand get to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:13.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kuzu hiitatte doujinai
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:16.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,What's essential is to have a strong mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:16.88,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kanjin nano strong na mind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:20.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,To outwit, and survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:20.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}dashinuite survive
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:26.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'm either gonna end up in Heaven or Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:26.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ikitsuku saki wa heaven or hell
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:33.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,There's just one rule in this world: the winner is always right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:33.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kono sekai no ruuru tatta hitotsu shousha koso ga seigi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:37.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,A woman's got to have guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:37.38,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}onna wa dokyou
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,Gotta keep him tantalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}jiresaseru no aitsu wo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:47.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything I can; I'm the compulsive gambling queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:47.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yareru koto nandatte yaru atashi wa kakegurui no kuiin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,Think you know my game; you doubt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}omitoshi sore you doubt me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,Make your read and let's showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yomikitte rettsu showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:54.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,Deal with the devil! I'll see through you and make you mine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:54.23,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}deal with the devil misukashite atashi no mono ni suru
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.60,Default2,,0,0,0,, from a single hair to your everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8} anata no kami no ippon made zenbu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:02.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,A million dollars? I say "raise". You're trembling, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:02.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}a million dollars? I'd say raise furueteruwayo bouya
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,I won't let you off this ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}orosase wa shinai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,Deal with the devil! Ah, the excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}deal with the devil uhhhnn koufun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,I can't get enough of these thrills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}tamaranai wa suriru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:11.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone touch this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:11.12,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}dare nimo sawarasenai kono money
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,A million dollars? I'd say "raise".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A million dollars? I'd say "raise".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.90,Default2,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:17.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,Come on, grit your teeth, start shaking, get excited! My heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:17.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}saa come on kakugo kimete furue takabure my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:21.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,You really look like you want it; you're still a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:21.30,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hoshigaru you jane mada beibii
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}dare nimo makenai
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,Let me feel it. Love me, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kanjisasete love me honey
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A gambling junkie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:30.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,I plan to dissolve the Student Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:35.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,{私は生徒会長を辞任し\N生徒会長選挙を行う}I will resign the Student Council presidency and hold an election.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.40,Default2,,0,0,0,,Are... are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.03,Default2,,0,0,0,,Holding an election
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:44.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,{あの蛇喰夢子によって連敗を喫した\Nこの状況で選挙など}after the council has suffered a string of defeats by Yumeko Jabami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:48.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,{自ら権力の座を\Nかなぐり捨てるようなもの}You would all but abandon your position of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.58,Default2,,0,0,0,,It is sheer folly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:56.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,Yuriko, you think you're in a position to criticize?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,How amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,Sheer folly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,is precisely my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.96,Default2,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.06,Default2,,0,0,0,,Hyakkao Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:10.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,is an aquarium of my own construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:15.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,{弱肉強食を理(ことわり)として\N美しく循環する閉じた世界}A beautifully cyclical, closed-off world based on the law of survival of the fittest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:20.60,Default2,,0,0,0,,{それをゆがませる輩(やから)が現れた}But someone has appeared who is distorting its beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:23.16,Default2,,0,0,0,,{水槽を喰(く)い荒らす輩が}They are devouring my aquarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:29.66,Default2,,0,0,0,,{その輩は 水槽に馴染(なじ)んだ者すら\N啓もうしていった}This person has brought enlightenment even to those who know nothing but the tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,{放っておけば ゆがみは大きくなり}If left to fester, the distortion will grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:36.55,Default2,,0,0,0,,{やがて\N手をつけられなくなるかもしれない}and may become too large to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:41.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,{だから 私は\Nもっともっと掻(か)き回したい}So I want to stir up the waters even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:56.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,If you would excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:21:01.09,Default2,,0,0,0,,As everyone has arrived, I have shown them to this chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:04.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（清華(さやか)）\N待ちなさい！\N今は重要な会議中ですよ}Stop right there. We are in the middle of an important meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:08.08,Default2,,0,0,0,,{許可なく 一般生徒が\N立ち入ることは禁止されています}Regular students are not allowed here without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:11.71,Default2,,0,0,0,,{はい 全て心得たうえでのことです}Yes. I am well aware of the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:15.21,Default2,,0,0,0,,{えっ… あなた 何者です？}Who... who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,{（零）\N私ごときが\N先に名乗るわけにはまいりません}It would not do for someone of my status to be introduced first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:24.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{等々喰(ととばみ)家より 定楽乃(てらの)様\Nそして ユミ様}Miss Terano and Miss Yumi of House Totobami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{和楽喰(わらくばみ)家より 淑光(すみか)様}Miss Sumika of House Warakubami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{陰喰(いんばみ)家より 三欲(みよ)様}Miss Miyo of House Inbami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:33.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,80)}{骨喰(ほねばみ)家より ミラスラーヴァ様}Miss Milaslava of House Honebami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:36.36,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,100)}{狛喰(こまばみ)家より 希(のぞみ)様}Miss Nozomi of House Komabami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:39.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{尾喰(おばみ)家より 凛(りん)様\Nそして 茨(いばら)様}Master Rin and Master Ibara of House Obami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:42.61,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{陽喰(ようばみ)家より 三理(みり)様}Miss Miri of House Yobami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:46.24,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{蟲喰家より 恵利美様にございます}And finally, Miss Erimi of House Mushibami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:49.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,{私は この方たちの\N学園生活を}I am here to facilitate the school lives
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,of these ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.70,Default2,,0,0,0,,{×喰(ばつばみ) 零と申します}My name is Rei Batsubami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.50,Default2,,0,0,0,,P-president, who are these people...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.87,Default2,,0,0,0,,This will be a pain to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:06.99,Default2,,0,0,0,,{あなた 代わりに\Nみんなに説明してちょうだい}Could you please explain it instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:14.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,{この方々は 本家当主たる\N桃喰(ももばみ)綺羅莉様に連なる 一族}These ladies and gentlemen are all relatives of Kirari Momobami, the head of the main family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:19.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,{一族は本家たる桃喰と\N多数の分家により構成されます}Their extended family consists of House Momobami and its many branch families.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:22.05,Default2,,0,0,0,,{ここにいる皆様は}All of them have
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:26.28,Default2,,0,0,0,,{それぞれの分家を代表して\N学園にいらっしゃった方々です}come to this academy as representatives of their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,{桃喰とは“百喰(ももばみ)”}"Momobami" also refers to the "Hundred Devourers".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:34.33,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,280)}{称して“百喰一族”}Together, they form the Momobami Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:42.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,{ようこそ 私の学園へ　そして…}Welcome to my academy. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.45,0:22:47.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,{弱肉強食の生徒会長選挙へ}To a presidential election in which only the fittest survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:12.10,ED,,0,0,0,,If you desire it so much as to writhe, I will give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:12.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}notautsu hodo ni motomeru no nara ataeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:16.40,ED,,0,0,0,,You will need to avail yourself of even your despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:16.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}zetsubou sae kate ni shite shimau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:19.71,ED,,0,0,0,,Now, come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:19.71,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}saa oide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:25.82,ED,,0,0,0,,If you offer your body and soul, I will answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:25.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mi mo kokoro mademo sashidasu nara kotaeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:31.42,ED,,0,0,0,,Tragedy will be overwhelmed by pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:31.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}higeki mo etsuraku ni nomareru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:39.07,ED,,0,0,0,,Consumed by an excess of pure carnal desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:39.07,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}amari nimo sekirara na retsujou ni ukasarenagara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:47.07,ED,,0,0,0,,Eventually you will live wishing only for a moment of titillation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:47.07,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yagate shibireru youna shunkan dake wo negai ikiru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:55.17,ED,,0,0,0,,O soul that burns with desire, raise your glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:55.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}aa katsubou suru tamashii yo sakazuki wo kakage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.17,0:24:01.94,ED,,0,0,0,,Sing an ode to such joy as will break you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.17,0:24:01.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kowareru hodo kanki no uta wo utaou
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:08.80,ED,,0,0,0,,Simple acclaim will never satisfy your cravings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:08.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kassai dewa michitaru hazu mo nai uzuki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.80,0:24:15.68,ED,,0,0,0,,It's maddening enough to bet on.
